title: Kurt Metzger
description: Kurt Metzger was so great on the live YMIW in NYC Pete had to grab him for a full one-on-one before he left and this is the hilarious and weird result. Kurt (Comedy Central, Ugly Americans) is one of Pete's favs (no surprise there) and after this, he's probably for sure gonna be one of yours too. GET INTO IT, WEIRDOS!!
